203.commit_message: Bug 1396797 Support for partials in manifest (#83)    Bug 1396797 Support for partials in manifest    The outbound manifest, used by balrog scriptworker, needs to  have information about partials added.    It's unwise to add a partial if there's no related complete,  so this involves a refactor so that instead of directly  populating context.balrog_manifest, we instead fill a  staging area with details about the files we have uploaded.    Once all uploads are done, we generate the balrog manifest  to be of the expected form.
